WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue(c.color9CD5FF) { color: #9CD5FF; }
::cue(c.colora8c7fa) { color: #a8c7fa; }

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:07.000 line:5% align:center
<b><c.color9CD5FF>One Pace Premium</c></b>
Keep the project alive: <c.colora8c7fa>ko-fi.com/not6ip</c>

2
00:01:43.650 --> 00:01:45.140
Shoot!

3
00:01:49.630 --> 00:01:51.790
There's not even a scratch on them!

4
00:01:51.790 --> 00:01:54.100
What's wrong with them?!

5
00:01:55.020 --> 00:01:56.440
Sanji!

6
00:01:56.860 --> 00:02:00.400
Take the injured guy
and get off of this island already.

7
00:02:01.020 --> 00:02:03.140
We don't need you here!

8
00:02:03.140 --> 00:02:04.990
They set us up.

9
00:02:04.990 --> 00:02:07.240
We'll make them pay!

10
00:02:07.240 --> 00:02:12.860
This whole island is Germa 66's target, Sanji!

11
00:02:12.860 --> 00:02:14.260
You guys!

12
00:02:14.770 --> 00:02:18.340
Are they really modified humans
with iron skins?!

13
00:02:18.340 --> 00:02:19.970
Bring me a bazooka!

14
00:02:23.650 --> 00:02:26.280
Germa!

15
00:02:26.280 --> 00:02:30.610
I thought that you were all dead!
How did you survive?!

16
00:02:30.610 --> 00:02:31.580
What do you mean?

17
00:02:31.580 --> 00:02:37.910
Ten thousand soldiers led by Nusstorte
took down your kingdom!

18
00:02:37.910 --> 00:02:41.540
Yeah, some flies swarmed around us,

19
00:02:41.540 --> 00:02:43.990
but we swatted
and dumped them in the sea.

20
00:02:43.990 --> 00:02:45.090
What?!

21
00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:49.770
Th-This is Mont d'Or! Answer me!

22
00:02:49.770 --> 00:02:53.270
Big Brother Nusstorte! Please answer!

23
00:02:53.270 --> 00:02:57.470
Big Brother Basskarte!
Big Brother Dosmarche!

24
00:02:57.470 --> 00:03:00.950
If anyone's there... answer me!

25
00:03:00.950 --> 00:03:04.700
Just as I feared, it's a series
of unexpected happenings,

26
00:03:04.700 --> 00:03:07.960
to include Pekoms' betrayal-vous plaît !

27
00:03:07.960 --> 00:03:14.040
Why did Germa's fleet
appear at Cacao Island-noir ?!

28
00:03:14.040 --> 00:03:18.920
What were you halfwits
going to do with our technology?

29
00:03:18.920 --> 00:03:21.360
You couldn't do a thing with it!

30
00:03:22.530 --> 00:03:25.510
You bastards!

31
00:03:25.510 --> 00:03:28.130
Sanji! Hurry and go!

32
00:03:28.130 --> 00:03:29.140
Yeah!

33
00:03:30.320 --> 00:03:34.530
Snack and the others are
under assault by Germa!

34
00:03:34.530 --> 00:03:36.520
Shouldn't we help them?!

35
00:03:36.520 --> 00:03:41.710
Don't get distracted by that!
We've gotta focus on Straw Hat's ship!

36
00:03:42.170 --> 00:03:44.810
Tell that to all ships around the island!

37
00:03:44.810 --> 00:03:45.900
Yes, ma'am!

38
00:03:48.020 --> 00:03:52.840
Mont d'Or and everyone else...
Germa must've outsmarted them!

39
00:03:52.840 --> 00:03:55.440
You were outsmarted too, Brother Daifuku.

40
00:03:55.440 --> 00:03:59.770
Tch! But I fought hard to catch up to you!

41
00:04:02.040 --> 00:04:04.460
<b>Peanuts Town
Nuts Island</b>

42
00:04:04.460 --> 00:04:07.620
Mama's hunger tantrum hasn't stopped yet!

43
00:04:07.620 --> 00:04:12.940
We live in an emperor's territory where we're supposed
to be protected in exchange for our lifespan.

44
00:04:12.940 --> 00:04:16.310
I can't believe the queen
destroyed this place.

45
00:04:16.310 --> 00:04:19.570
There's no way to remake the wedding cake

46
00:04:16.550 --> 00:04:22.570
<b>Beany-Bean Town
Munchie Island</b>

47
00:04:19.570 --> 00:04:24.700
that the famous Master Streusen took days to bake!

48
00:04:24.700 --> 00:04:30.620
Even Madam Pudding won't be able to
remake it in a mere several hours.

49
00:04:30.620 --> 00:04:34.370
The cake Mama craves...

50
00:04:30.750 --> 00:04:34.370
<b>Table Town
Cutlery Island</b>

51
00:04:34.370 --> 00:04:36.060
That's impossible!

52
00:04:36.060 --> 00:04:38.380
We should prepare to evacuate!

53
00:04:38.630 --> 00:04:44.130
<b>Sherbet Town
Ice Cream Island</b>

54
00:04:41.880 --> 00:04:45.870
Let's get out of here before Mama arrives!

55
00:04:45.870 --> 00:04:47.780
Where is Mama right now?!

56
00:04:47.780 --> 00:04:49.150
On Puffs Island!

57
00:04:49.150 --> 00:04:52.520
It's governed by the
minister of puffs, Madam Chiffon...

58
00:04:52.520 --> 00:04:55.720
The hungry Mama is coming to this island!

59
00:04:53.140 --> 00:04:57.400
<b>Puffs Island</b>

60
00:04:55.720 --> 00:04:57.400
Nothing will stop her!

61
00:04:57.400 --> 00:04:59.080
Madam Chiffon...

62
00:04:59.080 --> 00:05:02.360
Why did she bring the cake here?!

63
00:05:02.380 --> 00:05:04.980
Run!

64
00:05:11.490 --> 00:05:13.590
Hey, Jinbe!

65
00:05:13.590 --> 00:05:19.140
What do you think about Germa?
Are they friends or foes?

66
00:05:19.140 --> 00:05:23.730
They could've escaped already.
Why choose now to help us out?

67
00:05:23.730 --> 00:05:29.480
But... it's just for now that they're helping us, right?
So, how can we trust them?!

68
00:05:29.480 --> 00:05:32.650
Oh! Maybe Reiju-san came
to show me her panties...

69
00:05:41.010 --> 00:05:42.620
Hey, can you hear me?!

70
00:05:42.620 --> 00:05:46.790
Sanji! This is the closest
we can get to the island!

71
00:05:46.790 --> 00:05:50.580
I know!
Sail by the harbor at full speed!

72
00:05:50.580 --> 00:05:53.480
I'll get there while you're passing by!

73
00:05:53.480 --> 00:05:55.130
Sanji-kun ! How's Luffy?!

74
00:05:55.150 --> 00:06:00.010
I got him! I don't have time to talk now!
I'm counting on you, Nami-san !

75
00:06:00.010 --> 00:06:00.970
Okay!

76
00:06:03.620 --> 00:06:05.970
Let's go, Jinbe! To starboard!

77
00:06:05.970 --> 00:06:08.100
To starboard!

78
00:06:09.690 --> 00:06:11.740
Sanji!

79
00:06:11.740 --> 00:06:14.280
You can do it!

80
00:06:23.390 --> 00:06:25.780
Crush Germa!

81
00:06:25.780 --> 00:06:28.300
Where did Black Leg go?!

82
00:06:30.870 --> 00:06:32.750
I can't see because of the dust!

83
00:06:46.820 --> 00:06:48.370
There he is!

84
00:06:53.400 --> 00:06:55.060
Shoot him!

85
00:07:04.570 --> 00:07:06.990
Don't let him get away!

86
00:07:10.160 --> 00:07:14.580
That's right...
We cannot let him get away, no matter what!

87
00:07:15.790 --> 00:07:20.090
Straw Hat Luffy is...
the one person we cannot forgive!

88
00:07:24.750 --> 00:07:30.640
He didn't escape from Big Brother Katakuri
using dirty tricks...

89
00:07:31.380 --> 00:07:32.690
Big Sister Brûlée?!

90
00:07:33.330 --> 00:07:38.400
Do you wanna know
what really happened in the Mirro-world?

91
00:07:41.380 --> 00:07:43.000
Perfect!

92
00:07:43.000 --> 00:07:47.270
The strongest and best in the world!

93
00:07:48.050 --> 00:07:51.540
Our big brother, Katakuri...

94
00:07:55.210 --> 00:07:57.840
Big Brother...

95
00:08:05.490 --> 00:08:11.920
lost to Straw Hat Luffy!

96
00:08:24.450 --> 00:08:25.830
What?!

97
00:08:27.750 --> 00:08:29.960
Katakuri...

98
00:08:29.960 --> 00:08:32.250
Your legendary undefeated record...

99
00:08:33.090 --> 00:08:36.060
was broken by that pipsqueak?

100
00:08:37.720 --> 00:08:41.850
No way!

101
00:08:42.310 --> 00:08:44.680
There's no way our brother would lose!

102
00:08:44.680 --> 00:08:48.020
Commander Katakuri cannot be defeated!

103
00:08:48.020 --> 00:08:53.770
He must've used some kind of dirty trick!
That's unforgivable!

104
00:08:58.810 --> 00:09:01.900
Fill him with lead!

105
00:09:05.990 --> 00:09:08.740
Cut him into pieces!

106
00:09:14.670 --> 00:09:18.220
Smash Straw Hat Luffy to dust!

107
00:09:18.220 --> 00:09:20.090
Yeah!

108
00:09:37.400 --> 00:09:40.280
We won't let you escape, Straw Hat!

109
00:09:58.170 --> 00:10:00.220
Damn you!

110
00:10:00.250 --> 00:10:04.050
Straw Hat!

111
00:10:04.740 --> 00:10:06.480
I won't forgive you!

112
00:10:10.060 --> 00:10:13.350
Kill him, Big Brother Oven!

113
00:10:17.580 --> 00:10:19.080
Sparking...

114
00:10:22.260 --> 00:10:23.590
Valkyrie!

115
00:10:23.880 --> 00:10:25.920
Sparking

116
00:10:24.090 --> 00:10:25.920
Valkyrie

117
00:10:31.410 --> 00:10:32.470
Ichiji?!

118
00:10:33.350 --> 00:10:34.930
Take off, Sanji!

119
00:10:38.390 --> 00:10:41.210
Big Brother Oven! Are you okay?!

120
00:10:50.110 --> 00:10:52.120
Hand him over!

121
00:10:52.120 --> 00:10:54.410
Black Leg!

122
00:10:54.410 --> 00:10:56.910
I'm gonna take you down again!

123
00:11:18.210 --> 00:11:21.630
Winch Guillotine!

124
00:11:20.050 --> 00:11:22.720
Winch Guillotine

125
00:11:45.860 --> 00:11:47.240
Yonji?!

126
00:11:47.240 --> 00:11:49.030
Go!

127
00:11:52.900 --> 00:11:56.020
You're such an eyesore!

128
00:11:59.200 --> 00:12:02.130
Fire! He’s above the roofs!

129
00:12:03.820 --> 00:12:06.390
How dare you do that
to Commander Katakuri?!

130
00:12:21.360 --> 00:12:24.180
At this rate, you'll be filled with holes.

131
00:12:25.000 --> 00:12:26.390
Niji!

132
00:12:26.390 --> 00:12:28.060
Germa!

133
00:12:28.060 --> 00:12:29.430
Let's go!

134
00:12:32.770 --> 00:12:34.520
Lightspeed Sword!

135
00:12:42.770 --> 00:12:45.950
Henry Blazer!

136
00:12:44.070 --> 00:12:45.660
Henry

137
00:12:44.150 --> 00:12:45.660
Blazer

138
00:12:54.370 --> 00:12:59.190
Oh, no! Minister Oven!
Straw Hat Luffy is going to escape town!

139
00:12:59.190 --> 00:13:01.420
Escape town?!

140
00:13:09.320 --> 00:13:12.120
Goodbye, failure!

141
00:13:15.540 --> 00:13:18.680
Snack! Brownie! Joconde!

142
00:13:18.680 --> 00:13:21.090
Shoot them down at the harbor!

143
00:13:21.090 --> 00:13:23.090
They're coming toward you!

144
00:13:23.090 --> 00:13:25.550
Hey! Isn't someone talking to us
through the transponder snail?!

145
00:13:30.210 --> 00:13:32.700
I think I can make it!

146
00:13:32.700 --> 00:13:36.870
Don't let him go any further!
Prepare tear gas canisters!

147
00:13:38.200 --> 00:13:41.450
We should just take away his ability to fly!

148
00:13:53.150 --> 00:13:54.260
What's the matter?!

149
00:13:54.260 --> 00:13:56.010
Stay with us!

150
00:13:56.010 --> 00:13:58.070
Hey! Hey!

151
00:14:01.300 --> 00:14:02.860
Germa!

152
00:14:04.800 --> 00:14:07.240
Those who hurt my little brother...

153
00:14:08.680 --> 00:14:10.400
I won't forgive them!

154
00:14:12.150 --> 00:14:15.740
If I can... escape...

155
00:14:18.100 --> 00:14:19.740
here in the East Blue...

156
00:14:23.820 --> 00:14:26.310
I'll never...

157
00:14:26.310 --> 00:14:29.180
have to see...

158
00:14:29.180 --> 00:14:31.690
Father's face again, right?

159
00:14:39.800 --> 00:14:41.930
Pink Hornet!

160
00:14:45.060 --> 00:14:48.030
That's Straw Hat! Shoot!

161
00:14:52.270 --> 00:14:55.530
You're really a high-maintenance brother.

162
00:14:57.960 --> 00:15:00.670
Don't ever let him go!

163
00:15:01.390 --> 00:15:05.540
Sanji! You're a boy!
Stop crying already!

164
00:15:06.440 --> 00:15:10.150
Listen! Don't ever come back here!

165
00:15:10.150 --> 00:15:10.930
Uh-huh!

166
00:15:19.410 --> 00:15:22.460
Run!

167
00:15:22.460 --> 00:15:24.010
Don't look back!

168
00:15:28.350 --> 00:15:32.930
Sanji... My kid brother
and the kindest person in the world!

169
00:15:33.550 --> 00:15:34.560
Reiju!

170
00:15:35.980 --> 00:15:37.190
Goodbye!

171
00:15:57.150 --> 00:16:02.070
Straw Hat got off of the island!
Fleet, come in!

172
00:16:03.400 --> 00:16:06.950
Hurry up, Sanji!

173
00:16:12.710 --> 00:16:14.550
It's Sanji!

174
00:16:14.550 --> 00:16:16.510
Here he comes, everyone!

175
00:16:17.440 --> 00:16:20.010
Sanji is carrying Luffy!

176
00:16:22.010 --> 00:16:23.750
Yay!

177
00:16:23.750 --> 00:16:25.670
I knew Sanji could do it!

178
00:16:25.670 --> 00:16:26.980
Luffy!

179
00:16:30.780 --> 00:16:33.680
I can see it now, Luffy!
It's the Sunny !

180
00:16:34.210 --> 00:16:37.280
Is dinner ready yet, Sanji?

181
00:16:40.060 --> 00:16:43.920
<b>Mont d'Or's Tactical Operations Center
Sweet City, Whole Cake Island</b>

182
00:16:43.920 --> 00:16:46.000
Brother Peros!

183
00:16:46.000 --> 00:16:48.850
Please respond! How's Mama doing?!

184
00:16:48.850 --> 00:16:50.840
And what about Bege?! And the cake?!

185
00:16:50.840 --> 00:16:55.600
Depending on what you say, things might get even crazier on Cacao Island, Brother Peros!

186
00:16:56.220 --> 00:16:59.980
<b>Big Mom's Forces, At Sea</b>

187
00:16:57.050 --> 00:16:59.980
Please respond, Big Bro Peros!

188
00:16:59.980 --> 00:17:02.290
Yeah, I know!

189
00:17:04.990 --> 00:17:08.780
I still have my eyes
on Mama, Bege, and the others!

190
00:17:08.780 --> 00:17:11.720
Huh? What's wrong, Brother Peros?!

191
00:17:15.580 --> 00:17:18.580
Big Brother Mont d'Or! This is Bavarois!

192
00:17:18.580 --> 00:17:24.790
Brother Peros left his wound untreated for too long,
so he's losing his strength!

193
00:17:24.790 --> 00:17:26.020
What?!

194
00:17:26.020 --> 00:17:29.040
Now isn't the time to
worry about that... lick!

195
00:17:29.040 --> 00:17:30.170
Give me that!

196
00:17:32.450 --> 00:17:38.270
We’re near Puffs Island now! It’s pandemonium here, too!

197
00:17:38.270 --> 00:17:42.790
Chiffon and Bege finally dropped off the cake!

198
00:17:42.790 --> 00:17:47.140
The cake is on Puffs Island! Lick!

199
00:17:47.140 --> 00:17:50.890
In just a few minutes, this'll all be over!

200
00:17:51.610 --> 00:17:56.090
Even if that cake is laced
with deadly poison,

201
00:17:56.090 --> 00:17:58.920
there's no way for us to stop her anymore!

202
00:18:02.330 --> 00:18:06.570
There are three possible outcomes!

203
00:18:06.570 --> 00:18:07.940
First:

204
00:18:07.940 --> 00:18:10.280
By eating the poisoned cake,

205
00:18:11.480 --> 00:18:13.240
Mama dies!

206
00:18:21.190 --> 00:18:22.330
Second:

207
00:18:22.330 --> 00:18:24.650
The poison won't affect Mama,

208
00:18:24.650 --> 00:18:26.670
but the cake will taste bad!

209
00:18:26.670 --> 00:18:27.710
Yuck!

210
00:18:28.160 --> 00:18:33.550
In that case, it won't quell her hunger,
and she'll continue destroying the country!

211
00:18:33.550 --> 00:18:35.510
And third:

212
00:18:35.510 --> 00:18:39.030
The poison in the cake doesn't affect her
and it tastes good!

213
00:18:39.030 --> 00:18:43.360
It would take a miracle,
but it's the only way we can survive!

214
00:18:43.360 --> 00:18:45.730
Prepare yourselves!

215
00:18:45.730 --> 00:18:50.250
The taste of that cake will decide our fates!

216
00:18:52.670 --> 00:18:55.160
This is the worst situation ever-soir !

217
00:18:55.160 --> 00:18:58.120
Inform the entire country!

218
00:18:58.120 --> 00:18:59.750
They already know.

219
00:18:59.750 --> 00:19:02.400
Mama is out of control right now...

220
00:19:02.400 --> 00:19:05.350
I heard that Nuts Island
was completely devastated.

221
00:19:05.350 --> 00:19:06.040
What?!

222
00:19:06.040 --> 00:19:09.050
What's gonna happen to Totto Land?

223
00:19:09.050 --> 00:19:13.490
Our lives are on the line
with this cake-bon !

224
00:19:14.680 --> 00:19:18.220
Hey! Where did Morgans and Stussy go?!

225
00:19:18.220 --> 00:19:20.480
They left the island a while ago...

226
00:19:20.480 --> 00:19:21.770
What?!

227
00:19:21.770 --> 00:19:23.420
Capture them!

228
00:19:23.420 --> 00:19:28.610
If the worst result happens,
the news will leak to the outside world!

229
00:19:28.610 --> 00:19:29.490
Yes, sir!

230
00:19:30.240 --> 00:19:36.200
At the cost of all else,
that journalist must not leave the country!

231
00:19:36.200 --> 00:19:38.950
There's no telling what he could publish...

232
00:19:38.950 --> 00:19:42.870
This island is doomed!
Let's get out of here!

233
00:19:42.870 --> 00:19:47.210
Mama's gonna destroy it just like Nuts Island!

234
00:19:43.210 --> 00:19:47.210
<b>Fluffy Town, Puffs Island</b>

235
00:19:47.210 --> 00:19:51.920
Madam Chiffon was brainwashed
by the traitor, Bege!

236
00:19:55.550 --> 00:19:57.550
Chiffon! What are you saying?!

237
00:19:59.810 --> 00:20:04.980
I’m doing this because I believe in the cake Black Leg made.

238
00:20:05.490 --> 00:20:08.420
I don't know where he learned to cook...

239
00:20:08.420 --> 00:20:13.110
but his culinary skills surpass even those of the head chef!

240
00:20:16.990 --> 00:20:18.200
Vito! Gotti!

241
00:20:18.970 --> 00:20:22.590
You two go look for a ship to escape on!

242
00:20:22.590 --> 00:20:25.320
I'll bring Chiffon with me later!

243
00:20:25.320 --> 00:20:27.660
O-Okay-rero !

244
00:20:27.660 --> 00:20:28.990
Got it!

245
00:20:28.990 --> 00:20:31.950
We paid off our debt to the Straw Hats.

246
00:20:31.950 --> 00:20:34.330
We lost our precious ship.

247
00:20:34.330 --> 00:20:36.850
Those damn Straw Hats!

248
00:20:36.850 --> 00:20:40.420
They'd better not end up dead
after all we've done for them!

249
00:20:50.430 --> 00:20:52.890
Wedding...

250
00:21:00.320 --> 00:21:04.600
cake!

251
00:21:09.800 --> 00:21:13.290
Yay! They're back!

252
00:21:13.290 --> 00:21:14.600
Luffy!

253
00:21:14.600 --> 00:21:15.640
Sanji!

254
00:21:15.640 --> 00:21:16.630
Luffy-san !

255
00:21:16.630 --> 00:21:18.480
Luffy!

256
00:21:21.050 --> 00:21:23.020
I'm glad that you're okay!

257
00:21:23.020 --> 00:21:25.760
I'm so happy! Really!

258
00:21:27.440 --> 00:21:30.180
He's totally worn out...

259
00:21:31.270 --> 00:21:34.140
Well done! Luffy! Sanji!

260
00:21:34.140 --> 00:21:36.430
I was so worried, Luffy!

261
00:21:36.430 --> 00:21:38.600
Garchu!

262
00:21:40.750 --> 00:21:43.570
You guys kept me waiting so long!

263
00:21:43.570 --> 00:21:45.110
Yeah, right!

264
00:21:45.110 --> 00:21:48.280
Luffy... Did you beat Katakuri?

265
00:21:51.430 --> 00:21:52.410
Yeah!

266
00:21:52.410 --> 00:21:53.600
Wow!

267
00:21:53.600 --> 00:21:56.210
I'm so impressed, Luffy-san !

268
00:21:58.500 --> 00:21:59.420
He fell asleep?!

269
00:21:59.420 --> 00:22:01.890
His wounds are still fresh...

270
00:22:01.890 --> 00:22:06.980
Chopper-san, attend to his wounds!
He's losing too much blood, isn't he?!

271
00:22:06.980 --> 00:22:07.860
Yeah!

272
00:22:17.190 --> 00:22:20.250
Sanji, you too. You got shot!

273
00:22:21.570 --> 00:22:24.580
Oh, this is nothing.

274
00:22:31.600 --> 00:22:33.980
Good! We're finally in range.

275
00:22:36.410 --> 00:22:39.360
We didn’t notice them catching up!

276
00:22:39.360 --> 00:22:43.160
We haven't lost them yet!
Treat him as we sail away!

277
00:22:43.160 --> 00:22:44.600
Uh-huh!

278
00:23:05.260 --> 00:23:06.510
Fire!

279
00:23:19.650 --> 00:23:20.820
What the...?

280
00:23:27.350 --> 00:23:29.450
Germa's backing them up!

281
00:23:29.450 --> 00:23:31.370
Damn you, Judge!

282
00:23:32.100 --> 00:23:33.660
Should we return fire?!

283
00:23:33.660 --> 00:23:35.690
No, ignore them!

284
00:23:35.690 --> 00:23:39.210
Germa is also fighting
the fleet at the harbor!

285
00:23:39.210 --> 00:23:41.260
Aim at Straw Hat's ship!

286
00:23:41.260 --> 00:23:42.000
Yes, ma'am!

287
00:24:10.680 --> 00:24:14.660
Why do you care so much
about him, Straw Hat Luffy?!

288
00:24:16.580 --> 00:24:19.960
This is Emperor Big Mom's territory!

289
00:24:19.960 --> 00:24:23.040
You're in a place where escape
is impossible once you enter!

290
00:24:23.040 --> 00:24:27.510
And yet, you risked your life
just to take back one person?!

291
00:24:27.510 --> 00:24:31.320
Sanji is Germa's failure!

292
00:24:32.860 --> 00:24:35.920
He can't use his skin as a shield...

293
00:24:38.540 --> 00:24:43.120
He cooks because he doesn't
have a shred of royal pride!

294
00:24:44.210 --> 00:24:45.420
Uh-huh...

295
00:24:46.040 --> 00:24:48.840
He's an idiot with a soft spot...

296
00:24:49.880 --> 00:24:56.180
and a soft mind that makes him put his life on the line for the weak!

297
00:24:56.180 --> 00:25:00.930
He is truly unfit to be a soldier!

298
00:25:00.930 --> 00:25:03.410
That's all he is!

299
00:25:09.100 --> 00:25:11.810
Goodbye! Thank you for your help!

300
00:25:12.560 --> 00:25:14.850
Why don't you answer me?!

301
00:25:15.310 --> 00:25:17.480
Straw Hat!

302
00:25:17.920 --> 00:25:23.320
I'm surprised. Why did he suddenly start listing
all the good things about you?

303
00:25:23.320 --> 00:25:27.110
What?! He didn't mean it that way!

304
00:25:27.110 --> 00:25:28.210
What?!

305
00:25:31.470 --> 00:25:33.870
You guys are the best!

306
00:25:40.630 --> 00:25:42.190
Nami! Look ahead!

307
00:25:42.190 --> 00:25:43.570
What?

308
00:25:43.570 --> 00:25:45.690
No! This is terrible!

309
00:25:47.040 --> 00:25:50.630
Jinbe! There's a massive fleet
right in front of us!

310
00:25:50.630 --> 00:25:52.650
When did they get here?!

311
00:25:53.620 --> 00:25:55.530
Looks like they finally noticed...

312
00:25:56.990 --> 00:25:58.410
It's an entire armada!

313
00:25:58.410 --> 00:26:01.280
What should we do?
We're hemmed in again!

314
00:26:01.280 --> 00:26:08.210
The Sunny
Germa 66

315
00:26:02.040 --> 00:26:05.360
The idle fleet was able to circle around us!

316
00:26:02.620 --> 00:26:08.210
Cacao Island

317
00:26:06.320 --> 00:26:08.210
We're surrounded!

318
00:26:08.970 --> 00:26:11.920
We're already in their firing range!

319
00:26:11.920 --> 00:26:13.050
How?!

320
00:26:14.170 --> 00:26:15.480
That's right!

321
00:26:15.480 --> 00:26:18.640
We're coming from both the
front and back, rabbit!

322
00:26:18.640 --> 00:26:19.990
Carrot-chan !

323
00:26:19.990 --> 00:26:23.680
In front of you, a fleet...
behind you, a jinni!

324
00:26:23.680 --> 00:26:24.720
Jinni-uinely...

325
00:26:25.520 --> 00:26:27.480
Enraged Cleave!

326
00:26:27.500 --> 00:26:28.810
Black Leg?!

327
00:26:29.330 --> 00:26:30.230
Sanji!

328
00:26:32.760 --> 00:26:34.440
He's huge!

329
00:26:37.200 --> 00:26:41.620
You've finally entered the range of my ability!

330
00:26:41.620 --> 00:26:45.620
Now it looks like we're bullying them.

331
00:26:47.910 --> 00:26:50.330
How did they close in so quickly?!

332
00:26:50.330 --> 00:26:53.090
Look closely at the ships in front of us!

333
00:26:57.300 --> 00:27:00.240
They're all paddle ships!

334
00:27:01.590 --> 00:27:02.490
No way!

335
00:27:02.490 --> 00:27:04.470
There's no way we can escape!

336
00:27:04.470 --> 00:27:09.690
I guess this is the end! We were barely able to make it this far, but...

337
00:27:09.690 --> 00:27:11.660
Crush them!

338
00:27:18.790 --> 00:27:20.100
What's going on?!

339
00:27:24.980 --> 00:27:27.350
The surface of the sea is swelling up...

340
00:27:28.560 --> 00:27:34.160
I won't forgive anyone who...

341
00:27:35.560 --> 00:27:40.600
gives the boss any trouble!

342
00:27:45.210 --> 00:27:46.960
What?!

343
00:27:46.960 --> 00:27:50.590
That guy... he was a member
of Hody's crew on Fishman Island...

344
00:27:50.590 --> 00:27:52.520
Wadatsumi!

345
00:27:53.840 --> 00:27:54.680
What?

346
00:27:55.050 --> 00:27:55.970
No way!

347
00:27:55.970 --> 00:27:57.930
Jinbe!

348
00:28:02.860 --> 00:28:04.320
You guys!

349
00:28:08.990 --> 00:28:13.600
We came to see you off, Captain Jinbe!

350
00:28:13.600 --> 00:28:16.370
Ah, that's "former"! Former Captain!

351
00:28:23.080 --> 00:28:28.840
Until you get out of Big Mom’s territory, we’re still your crew… all right?!

352
00:28:30.360 --> 00:28:32.170
I got it!

353
00:28:33.630 --> 00:28:36.130
Go away!

354
00:28:36.130 --> 00:28:37.920
So cool!

355
00:28:40.260 --> 00:28:42.120
W-What the...?!

356
00:28:42.120 --> 00:28:43.810
It's flooded!

357
00:28:45.640 --> 00:28:48.350
Someone punched holes in the bottom?!

358
00:28:49.380 --> 00:28:51.480
There are fishmen in the water!

359
00:28:51.480 --> 00:28:53.690
How are they so sneaky?!

360
00:28:53.690 --> 00:28:56.480
Come out, you damn fishmen!

361
00:29:03.550 --> 00:29:05.620
You bastards!

362
00:29:09.210 --> 00:29:10.250
Damn!

363
00:29:10.250 --> 00:29:12.380
I won't let the Straw Hats get away!

364
00:29:14.340 --> 00:29:16.750
Jinni!

365
00:29:18.630 --> 00:29:20.050
Ocean Current...

366
00:29:20.110 --> 00:29:23.140
Shoulder Throw!

367
00:29:43.030 --> 00:29:43.990
Look!

368
00:29:47.380 --> 00:29:49.560
A path opened on the sea!

369
00:30:02.330 --> 00:30:05.840
Push forward while we
hold them off, Captain Jinbe!

370
00:30:05.840 --> 00:30:10.260
We won't let you
harm the Straw Hats' ship!

371
00:30:16.140 --> 00:30:18.100
Thank you!

372
00:30:18.720 --> 00:30:21.130
Why didn't I notice?

373
00:30:21.130 --> 00:30:26.980
They disabled the enemy's
territorial sea slugs for us, too.

374
00:30:26.980 --> 00:30:30.780
They ended up helping me to the very end.

375
00:30:30.780 --> 00:30:34.620
As expected of Jinbe's crew!

376
00:30:34.620 --> 00:30:36.270
Yeah!

377
00:30:36.270 --> 00:30:38.170
Thanks...

378
00:30:38.170 --> 00:30:40.120
you guys!

379
00:30:40.120 --> 00:30:44.960
Take care of Jinbe for us, Straw Hat!

380
00:30:44.960 --> 00:30:46.360
Okay!

381
00:30:49.920 --> 00:30:51.670
Fire!

382
00:30:55.640 --> 00:30:57.130
Merge!

383
00:31:11.230 --> 00:31:15.440
Minister Oven,
shouldn't you be on Cacao Island?!

384
00:31:16.360 --> 00:31:20.650
I left Germa to Brûlée!

385
00:31:21.070 --> 00:31:24.670
These are heavy-metal
composite bullets that can easily

386
00:31:24.670 --> 00:31:27.740
punch holes through
Germa's raid suits!

387
00:31:27.740 --> 00:31:30.500
Go teach them a lesson!

388
00:31:30.500 --> 00:31:31.290
Yes, ma'am!

389
00:31:43.340 --> 00:31:45.300
It's that guy again!

390
00:31:48.220 --> 00:31:51.100
Straw Hat!

391
00:31:54.940 --> 00:31:58.860
Since you brought down Katakuri,
you're the last person...

392
00:31:58.860 --> 00:32:00.820
I'd ever let leave alive!

393
00:32:10.270 --> 00:32:11.960
What's gonna happen?

394
00:32:20.940 --> 00:32:24.270
Don't worry. It's gonna be alright!

395
00:32:24.270 --> 00:32:26.510
The man who baked it....

396
00:32:26.510 --> 00:32:28.350
is a true chef!

397
00:32:29.820 --> 00:32:33.520
Wait, Black Leg!
Won’t that method take all night?

398
00:32:33.520 --> 00:32:35.430
Taking this time is vital.

399
00:32:35.430 --> 00:32:37.100
But we don't have time!

400
00:32:37.100 --> 00:32:38.710
I'll do it in two hours!

401
00:32:38.710 --> 00:32:40.540
You're kidding!

402
00:32:41.990 --> 00:32:46.180
Why are you smiling?!
Get serious, Black Leg!

403
00:32:47.020 --> 00:32:51.860
Your ship and our country are at stake!

404
00:32:52.950 --> 00:32:54.270
I'm sorry...

405
00:32:55.000 --> 00:32:57.020
I just couldn't help thinking about...

406
00:32:57.020 --> 00:33:00.490
Big Mom's delighted face
as she calls this cake "delicious."

407
00:33:01.080 --> 00:33:02.470
How lovely!

408
00:33:02.470 --> 00:33:03.830
Her delighted face?!

409
00:33:03.830 --> 00:33:06.760
Don't you realize that your life is in danger?

410
00:33:16.930 --> 00:33:18.320
Mama!

411
00:33:21.900 --> 00:33:24.040
Did the poison kill her?!

412
00:33:34.920 --> 00:33:40.370
It's so delicious...
that I could die right now!

413
00:33:40.370 --> 00:33:43.120
The sweetness is unbelievable!

414
00:33:46.460 --> 00:33:50.840
This is it!

415
00:33:50.840 --> 00:33:55.760
The wedding cake!

416
00:33:58.200 --> 00:33:59.910
She stopped...

417
00:33:59.910 --> 00:34:01.300
What about the poison?!

418
00:34:01.300 --> 00:34:06.440
I'm sure it was in there!
It just didn't work! That's our Mama!

419
00:34:10.250 --> 00:34:12.610
Black Leg!

420
00:34:12.610 --> 00:34:15.190
That's the look that you wished to see!

421
00:34:15.920 --> 00:34:19.730
♪ It's superb! This sweetness! ♪

422
00:34:19.730 --> 00:34:23.300
♪ I know I've tasted it somewhere! ♪

423
00:34:23.300 --> 00:34:29.100
It's delicious!

424
00:34:32.710 --> 00:34:36.230
To all islands of Totto Land...

425
00:34:36.230 --> 00:34:40.130
the damage will spread no further!

426
00:34:47.220 --> 00:34:51.300
Because of the efforts of the
Charlotte family's 35th daughter, Pudding,

427
00:34:51.300 --> 00:34:54.180
Mama's ravenous rampage has been quelled!

428
00:34:54.180 --> 00:34:59.080
Thank goodness! I thought this island would be next,
since we're so close to Cacao Island!

429
00:34:59.080 --> 00:35:01.010
It was scary!

430
00:35:01.010 --> 00:35:02.610
We're okay now!

431
00:35:03.000 --> 00:35:05.040
Thank you, Bege!

432
00:35:16.500 --> 00:35:23.230
By using Madam Chiffon, who betrayed the country,
Madam Pudding saved Totto Land!

433
00:35:23.230 --> 00:35:24.990
No one else could do it!

434
00:35:24.990 --> 00:35:27.520
Thank you, Madam Pudding!

435
00:35:27.520 --> 00:35:30.370
That's our Madam Pudding!

436
00:35:30.370 --> 00:35:31.780
No...

437
00:35:32.270 --> 00:35:33.890
It wasn't me.

438
00:35:41.120 --> 00:35:42.940
Bring it on!

439
00:35:51.180 --> 00:35:54.390
Sparking Figure!

440
00:36:02.320 --> 00:36:04.610
Hot Sea Hell!

441
00:36:17.170 --> 00:36:20.210
Everyone, swim deeper into the sea!

442
00:36:20.210 --> 00:36:23.590
It's too hot! I can't get near him!

443
00:36:24.440 --> 00:36:27.080
There is no protection for you guys!

444
00:36:27.080 --> 00:36:29.470
And you have nowhere to run!

445
00:36:33.470 --> 00:36:34.470
Dammit!

446
00:36:34.470 --> 00:36:37.100
What should we do, Luffy?!

447
00:36:43.670 --> 00:36:45.000
Let's...

448
00:36:46.560 --> 00:36:47.790
advance!

449
00:36:51.180 --> 00:36:55.120
The Queen Mama Chanter will be
arriving at Cacao Island soon.

450
00:36:59.170 --> 00:37:03.050
Alright! Just in time!

451
00:37:10.760 --> 00:37:12.390
Fluffy!

452
00:37:12.890 --> 00:37:14.560
Munch!

453
00:37:14.560 --> 00:37:16.350
Gulp!

454
00:37:18.980 --> 00:37:19.940
♪ Fluffy! ♪

455
00:37:19.940 --> 00:37:20.980
♪ Munch! ♪

456
00:37:20.980 --> 00:37:21.900
♪ Gulp! ♪

457
00:37:23.020 --> 00:37:23.820
♪ Fluffy! ♪

458
00:37:23.820 --> 00:37:24.940
♪ Munch! ♪

459
00:37:24.940 --> 00:37:25.900
♪ Gulp! ♪

460
00:37:27.320 --> 00:37:28.350
♪ What... ♪

461
00:37:29.200 --> 00:37:30.170
♪ is this?! ♪

462
00:37:30.870 --> 00:37:34.790
♪ Dreamy... taste? ♪

463
00:37:32.920 --> 00:37:34.790
♪ Flower! Flower! ♪

464
00:37:34.790 --> 00:37:38.970
♪ It's something that's beyond my wildest dreams! ♪

465
00:37:38.970 --> 00:37:42.970
♪ I can't even find the words to describe it! ♪

466
00:37:42.970 --> 00:37:44.890
♪ What? What? ♪

467
00:37:44.890 --> 00:37:46.930
♪ What's this flavor? ♪

468
00:37:46.930 --> 00:37:50.940
♪ It's making rotten puppies start dancing! ♪

469
00:37:50.940 --> 00:37:53.910
♪ The flavor is concentrated like... ♪

470
00:37:53.910 --> 00:37:59.880
♪ ...a pet cemetery! ♪

471
00:38:10.870 --> 00:38:13.010
♪ It's sweet! ♪

472
00:38:11.960 --> 00:38:13.850
♪ It's sweet... ♪

473
00:38:13.010 --> 00:38:15.050
♪ It's milky! ♪

474
00:38:13.870 --> 00:38:15.890
♪ It's milky... ♪

475
00:38:15.050 --> 00:38:21.180
♪ It's very rich and... ♪

476
00:38:22.430 --> 00:38:24.980
♪ risky! ♪

477
00:38:31.060 --> 00:38:36.980
♪ Look! Yes, it's a big fuss! ♪

478
00:38:35.020 --> 00:38:36.980
♪ Ship! Ship! ♪

479
00:38:36.980 --> 00:38:41.030
♪ It's like when you throw a bomb... ♪

480
00:38:41.030 --> 00:38:46.070
♪ into an amusement park! ♪

481
00:38:49.990 --> 00:38:52.070
♪ Like your stomach is having... ♪

482
00:38:52.070 --> 00:38:57.130
♪ ...a big ceremony! ♪

483
00:39:03.220 --> 00:39:06.760
♪ Hey, Mother... ♪

484
00:39:06.760 --> 00:39:15.940
♪ can you taste this overflowing happy sweetness? ♪

485
00:39:18.230 --> 00:39:18.980
"Happy birthday, Linlin"

486
00:39:18.980 --> 00:39:20.270
Oh, yeah!

487
00:39:20.320 --> 00:39:24.710
♪ It's the flavor of happiness... ♪

488
00:39:20.520 --> 00:39:32.790
"Happy birthday, Linlin"

489
00:39:24.710 --> 00:39:29.990
♪ from back then! ♪

490
00:39:29.990 --> 00:39:32.790
Happy birthday,

491
00:39:32.790 --> 00:39:35.080
Linlin!

492
00:39:36.960 --> 00:39:45.010
♪ Let's eat again together someday! ♪

493
00:39:45.010 --> 00:39:46.870
♪ It's sweet! ♪

494
00:39:45.930 --> 00:39:48.160
♪ It's sweet... ♪

495
00:39:46.870 --> 00:39:48.970
♪ It's milky! ♪

496
00:39:48.320 --> 00:39:50.530
♪ It's milky... ♪

497
00:39:48.970 --> 00:39:56.520
♪ It's very rich and... ♪

498
00:39:56.660 --> 00:40:00.020
♪ risky! ♪

499
00:40:13.240 --> 00:40:17.040
Hey, Mother, do you think...

500
00:40:17.040 --> 00:40:19.120
I can do this?

501
00:40:20.940 --> 00:40:25.210
♪ Everyone's happy! ♪

502
00:40:25.210 --> 00:40:28.940
♪ It's a peaceful utopia! ♪

503
00:40:28.940 --> 00:40:37.130
♪ It doesn't discriminate by race! ♪

504
00:40:37.130 --> 00:40:44.430
♪ If you try to leave, I'll kill you, though... ♪

505
00:40:44.430 --> 00:40:48.910
♪ It's a devilish contract! ♪

506
00:40:48.910 --> 00:40:53.070
♪ The peaceful Totto Land! ♪

507
00:40:53.070 --> 00:40:56.820
♪ We're all family! ♪

508
00:40:56.820 --> 00:41:01.840
♪ The gentle queen... ♪

509
00:41:02.620 --> 00:41:03.950
♪ Big Mom! ♪

510
00:41:16.930 --> 00:41:19.040
♪ It was delicious! ♪

511
00:41:19.040 --> 00:41:22.090
♪ Thank you for the meal... ♪
